17
00:01:41,062 --> 00:01:45,095
Host: a concern he raised while seconded to the Ministry of Defence.

18
00:01:46,563 --> 00:01:52,587
Games Master: job was to try to alert colleagues to what was going on and where the gaps were.

19
00:01:52,672 --> 00:01:57,953
