22
00:02:13,276 --> 00:02:25,055
Host: Resilience was second nature during the Cold War, but when the Soviet Union collapsed, successive Prime Ministers spent less on the armed forces and more on other priorities.

23
00:02:25,645 --> 00:02:36,344
Host: European allies did the same, all seeing this as a peace dividend, while gambling that the United States would still protect them if things went wrong.

24
00:02:40,478 --> 00:02:44,005
Host: the threat posed by Russia never really went away

25
00:02:44,495 --> 00:02:46,081
