27
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,586
Guest: think it's common sense, right?

28
00:02:54,788 --> 00:02:58,028
Guest: If they don't pay, I'm not going to defend them now, I'm not going to defend them.

29
00:02:59,733 --> 00:03:01,032
